# The diffusion model configs are read byte-for-byte alongside the .onnx blobs they describe; keep git
# from normalising their line endings (it silently changed world_pipeline_config.json from 774 to 817
# bytes on checkout, which the loader's size check then read as a corrupt download).
Assets/TerrainDiffusion/*.json -text
